-- South African Rand Strength a Challenge, Industry Minister Rob Davies Says
-- B y   M i k e   C o h e n
-- 2010-09-21T07:39:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/south-african-rand-strength-a-challenge-industry-minister-rob-davies-says.html
The strength of the South African
rand is a challenge for the economy and the central’s bank’s
decision to cut interest rates was correct, Rob Davies, the
country’s industry minister, told businessman in Durban today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mike Cohen in Cape Town at 
 mcohen21@bloomberg.net  